commit.message:
icons: Add bundled fallback icon

When there is no icon set installed (or no symbolic icon name can be
resolved), the Qt would rant "QSystemTrayIcon::setVisible: No Icon set".
For such cases we bundle some humble icon and rather use that instead of
null icon.
